About this item

  • 11000 Hours Lifespan - Each bulb is expected to last over 10 years (based on 3 hours/day), saving you the cost and hassle of frequent bulb replacement.
  • Energy Efficient - Replaces 100W incandescent bulb with 14W LED and saves you 86% in energy use, making it an economical alternative to incandescent bulbs.
  • Standard E26 Base - Easily screw into any light fixture with medium screw base. Widely used in table lamps, floor lamps and open pendant fixtures for bedroom, living room, dining room or anywhere for home or commercial use.
  • Energizing Daylight - With a color temperature of 5000 kelvin, these LED bulbs provide a calm and comfortable white light for any room.
  • What You Get - 6 Non-dimmable A19 E26 LED bulbs. (Not eligible for shipments to California.)

    Product Description

    Read more

    Standard A19 E26 LED Bulbs, Compact Yet Bright

    • 14-Watt LED bulbs replace 100-Watt incandescent bulbs.
    • Replace your old incandescent bulbs for a brighter and energy-friendly home.

    Extremely Long Life

    • LED bulbs can last up to 11,000 hours, much longer than incandescent and halogen bulbs, saving your effort and money in replacing bulbs constantly.

    Safe for Home Use

    • Instant on with full brightness. No flicker. No harsh glare.
    • Mercury free, lead free. No UV/IR light.
    • 80+ CRI brings out the true colors of your interior.

    Specifications

    • Wattage: 14W=100W
    • Brightness: 1600lm
    • Color Temperature: 5000K Daylight
    • Non-dimmable
    • Diameter: 2.36in/60mm
    • Height: 4.56in/116mm
    • A19 Shape, E26 Base
    • Lifespan: 11000 hours
    Read more

    Energy Saving

    • Replacing 100W incandescent bulb by 14W LED will save you 86% on electricity bill.

    Wide Beam Angle

    • 180 degree flood beam angle provides diffused and uniform lighting, perfect for both up lighting and down lighting fixtures in living room, bedroom, kitchen, garage, study or office.

    Soft on Eyes

    • With a color temperature of 5000 kelvin, these LED bulbs provide a calm and comfortable white light for any room.
    • CRI is over 80, which means more vivid and natural light.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
